1. cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper deals with the performance analysis of a precoding technique in a multi-user MISO system, which is a common topic in information theory. 
2. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper considers a multi-user system and analyzes the performance of the precoding technique, which can be seen as a problem in multi-agent systems. 
3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with the downlink of a wireless communication system, which is a topic in networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper considers a multi-user system, which can be seen as a social network, and analyzes the performance of the precoding technique. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with the performance analysis of a wireless communication system, which can be seen as a multimedia system.
